title: This Olympic Gold Medalist Had the Best Bridal Photo Shoot in the Bahamas
text:
Whatâ€™s better than being happily engaged, laid up on the beach, and catching some good sun rays? An epic photo shoot with your bridesmaids, of course. Olympic gold medalist, Shaunae Miller, poses with bridesmaid in epic photoshoot (Photo courtesy of Stanlo Photography). More Bride-to-be Shaunae Miller, an Olympic gold medalist who won in the 400 mm event in the Rio Olympics in 2016, posed alongside her fellow #Squad during their Bahamian bachelorette vacation. The Bahamian native returned to her roots. The photos? Flawless.
